{"tid":1432664,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「裝備撚」 係時候討論下防割裝備","createTime":"2019-08-08T09:39:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T10:44:26.000Z","uid":302618,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6ae5a050cd73f0b21444726bd80d095ba6b7fd1b","tid":1432664,"uid":302618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:39:03.000Z","msg":"P 牌仔第一次出 post, 如有唔識規距請溫柔地屌<br />\n<br />\n有見對家除左棍之外， 仲出埋槌仔同刀， 而且會突然出手， 防不勝防， 於是在下就上網睇下有咩防具可以日常帶定出街又能夠提升防禦力<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1）足球護脛<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mPz1QDb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmPz1QDb.png&h=7a719137&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好處： 價錢平， 易買到， 前臂同小腿兼用， 體積重量容易塞入袋， 被狗逗時易解釋<br />\n缺點： 要諗方法（例如長襪， 護膝）固定， 防力有限 （在下用自己立棍打自己既方式實測，要兩層才無咁痛， 刀未試）， 因長度關係只提供提供有限範圍既保護<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2） 防割手袖 / 護臂<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/51Bkp6zeX-L._AC_AA160_.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-na.ssl-images-amazon.com%2Fimages%2FI%2F51Bkp6zeX-L._AC_AA160_.jpg&d=g7cViP25SqI%2F%2FE6cIGpO7%2BSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=dfd0bfb3\" target=\"_blank\">https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/51Bkp6zeX-L._AC_AA160_.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n例如呢種 ： <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Kevlar-Sleeves-Limerense-Protection-Lightweight/dp/B07982K3C5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FKevlar-Sleeves-Limerense-Protection-Lightweight%2Fdp%2FB07982K3C5&d=g7cViP25SqI%2F%2FE6cIGpO7%2BSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=ff88a01f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.com/Kevlar-Sleeves-Limerense-Protection-Lightweight/dp/B07982K3C5</a><br />\n<br />\n好處： 較護脛容易融入日常衣著，無固定形狀所以容易塞入袋， 重量輕， 普遍較護脛長所以可以 cover 較長範圍包埋手踭， 無需額外固定<br />\n<br />\n缺點： 香港唔知有無得賣， 可能要需時去外國訂， 只防刀， 對棍零防<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3） 防割頸套<br />\n<br />\n例如呢種 ： <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Scratch-Resistant-Kevlar-Neck-Protector/dp/B07CNJ8TY3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FScratch-Resistant-Kevlar-Neck-Protector%2Fdp%2FB07CNJ8TY3&d=g7cViP25SqI%2F%2FE6cIGpO7%2BSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=295caf7f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.com/Scratch-Resistant-Kevlar-Neck-Protector/dp/B07CNJ8TY3</a><br />\n<br />\n好處： 冬天時容易融入日常衣著，無固定形狀所以容易塞入袋， 重量輕， 無需額外固定<br />\n<br />\n缺點： 夏天會熱， 會被眼望望， 香港唔知有無得賣， 可能要需時去外國訂， 只防刀， 對棍零防， 價錢就見仁見智啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4） 扮 cap 帽的安全帽<br />\n<br />\n例如呢種： <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Titus-Lightweight-Safety-Bump-Cap/dp/B07CP4DV75\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FTitus-Lightweight-Safety-Bump-Cap%2Fdp%2FB07CP4DV75&d=g7cViP25SqI%2F%2FE6cIGpO7%2BSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=d45ef127\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.com/Titus-Lightweight-Safety-Bump-Cap/dp/B07CP4DV75</a><br />\n<br />\n或者呢種 ： <a href=\"https://hken.rs-online.com/web/c/safety-security-esd-control-clean-room/personal-protection-equipment/bump-caps-safety-caps/?pn=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhken.rs-online.com%2Fweb%2Fc%2Fsafety-security-esd-control-clean-room%2Fpersonal-protection-equipment%2Fbump-caps-safety-caps%2F%3Fpn%3D2&d=g7cViP25SqI%2F%2FE6cIGpO7%2BSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=615c5dc3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hken.rs-online.com/web/c/safety-security-esd-control-clean-room/personal-protection-equipment/bump-caps-safety-caps/?pn=2</a><br />\n<br />\n好處： 較黃色安全帽容易融入日常衣著， 香港都有得訂<br />\n<br />\n缺點： 防力有限， 通常無帽帶無得綁實個頭（驚易甩）， 價錢自己諗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n5） 其他<br />\n<br />\n5.1） 有墊背心， 例如 ： <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/ThreeH-Protective-Tactical-Military-Equipment/dp/B077YC8MV2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FThreeH-Protective-Tactical-Military-Equipment%2Fdp%2FB077YC8MV2&d=g7cViP25SqI%2F%2FE6cIGpO7%2BSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=e01a8fc5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.com/ThreeH-Protective-Tactical-Military-Equipment/dp/B077YC8MV2</a><br />\n<br />\n5.2） 電單車防具， 例如： <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Motorcycle-Protection-Motocross-Racing-Protective/dp/B07H4FRJ82\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FMotorcycle-Protection-Motocross-Racing-Protective%2Fdp%2FB07H4FRJ82&d=g7cViP25SqI%2F%2FE6cIGpO7%2BSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=32b91507\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.com/Motorcycle-Protection-Motocross-Racing-Protective/dp/B07H4FRJ82</a><br />\n<br />\n5.3） 單車防具， 例如： <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/JBM-Guards-Protective-Cycling-Protection/dp/B016U4R5J8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FJBM-Guards-Protective-Cycling-Protection%2Fdp%2FB016U4R5J8&d=g7cViP25SqI%2F%2FE6cIGpO7%2BSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=29d78736\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.com/JBM-Guards-Protective-Cycling-Protection/dp/B016U4R5J8</a><br />\n<br />\n以上三樣， 我諗日常好難帶定出街<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因對家隨時發癲， 小弟以上純粹拋豬腩肉， 各位手足有咩諗法希望可以一齊討論下"},{"pid":"14947cf3f4af999088a92bd7aefbc9c8fa6edbc0","tid":1432664,"uid":302618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:58:56.000Z","msg":"可以參考下， 關於唔同物料特性既介紹<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/K4QA-MvAKqk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FK4QA-MvAKqk&d=g7cViP25SqI%2F%2FE6cIGpO7%2BSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=e7bbeab7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/K4QA-MvAKqk</a>"},{"pid":"8786780be880b87498c88c9e2ad44d563c3f3f44","tid":1432664,"uid":33274,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T12:19:42.000Z","msg":"有用要推"},{"pid":"931956d37af1a085e7c3f54e77c2b9b584297ac6","tid":1432664,"uid":156017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T12:21:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aa6fdc2d61474923e258b8d57a64c3532f6f00b5","tid":1432664,"uid":15345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T15:14:02.000Z","msg":"隻帽好似幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 